      <title>香港编辑因首起媒体煽动案被判入狱 21 个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/hong-kong-editor-jailed-21-months-in-first-media-sedition-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港法院以发表有关民主活动人士的文章为由判处一名前编辑 21 个月监禁，这是香港回归中国以来第一名因煽动叛乱罪而入狱的记者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/hong-kong-editor-jailed-21-months-in-first-media-sedition-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:13:53 GMT</pubDate>
