    <item>
      <title>特朗普寻求还清每天高达 11.2 万美元的最大债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/trump-seeks-to-wipe-out-his-biggest-debt-costing-112-000-a-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的律师正在执行一项任务，即消除他最大的财务负担——一项近 5 亿美元的欺诈判决，该判决的金额每天飙升约 10 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/trump-seeks-to-wipe-out-his-biggest-debt-costing-112-000-a-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛策略师称美国大选将考验股市乐观情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/goldman-strategists-say-us-election-to-test-optimism-in-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团的策略师表示，美国股市自夏季抛售后有所复苏，但这场关系重大的总统大选可能会扰乱投资者对美国股市的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/goldman-strategists-say-us-election-to-test-optimism-in-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
